data.description: This is the One ! Fabulous 4 bed 3 bath home with a pool/spa in the heart of Henderson. This 2 story home is located on a corner lot. The spacious primary bedroom and bath are located on the main floor and includes a custom walk in closet. Large loft, den and 3 additional bedrooms are located upstairs. Kitchen includes granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets and a large island.  EVEN MORE upgrades include shutters throughout the main floor, Kenitico water softner/reverse osmosis, solar screens and solar power pool heater. Also includes multiple SMART home outlets, electronic air filters and  NEST Thermostat. Newer Goettl AC Units 2017 and 2018. Centrally located, close to shopping and restaurants. The perfect place to call home.
